    <fr:title text="Projection functions and surjections › "><fr:link href="jms-00MC.xml" title="Projection functions and surjections" addr="jms-00MC" type="local">Projection functions and <fr:link href="jms-00M8.xml" title="Surjection" addr="jms-00M8" type="local">surjections</fr:link></fr:link> › </fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>Suppose that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\pi _1\colon  A\times  B\to  A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="jms-00M8.xml" title="Surjection" addr="jms-00M8" type="local">surjective</fr:link>. We proceed by cases on whether <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is empty:</fr:p>
 <fr:ol><fr:li>If <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is empty, we are done.</fr:li>
  <fr:li>If <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is inhabited by some <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex>, then by assumption there exists <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u\in  A\times  B]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\pi _1{\mathopen {}\left (u\right )\mathclose {}}=a]]></fr:tex>. Thus <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> is inhabited by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\pi _2{\mathopen {}\left (u\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:li></fr:ol>

 <fr:p>Conversely, suppose that either <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B\not =\varnothing ]]></fr:tex> or <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A=\varnothing ]]></fr:tex>. Fixing <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex>, we must show that there exists <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u\in  A\times  B]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\pi _1{\mathopen {}\left (u\right )\mathclose {}}=a]]></fr:tex>. If <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A=\varnothing ]]></fr:tex>, then we have a contradiction already; on the other hand, if there exists any <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b\in  B]]></fr:tex>, we may define <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u:={\mathopen {}\left (a,b\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> and we are done.</fr:p>
</fr:mainmatter>
