            <fr:taxon>Example</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>The projection function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\pi _1\colon  A\times  B\to  A]]></fr:tex> sending <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (a,b\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="jms-00M8.xml" title="Surjection" addr="jms-00M8" type="local">surjective</fr:link> if and only if either <html:span style="white-space: nowrap" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B \not =\varnothing ]]></fr:tex></html:span> or <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A=\varnothing ]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
